casebody.data:
Gilberto ISAAC, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Suzette LAGE, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1599 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 25, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated August 20, 2018, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
